This is a list of '''planned commercial [[LTE (telecommunication)|Long-Term Evolution]] (LTE) networks''' around the world, grouped by their frequency bands.

Some operators utilize multiple bands and are therefore listed multiple times in respective sections.

{{TOClimit|limit=2}}

== General information ==
* For technical details on LTE and a list of its designated operating frequencies, bands, and roaming possibilities, see [[LTE frequency bands]].
* Bands 33 to 44 are assigned to [[Time-Division Long-Term Evolution|TD-LTE]].

